    *   [General sanctions](/Wikipedia:General_sanctions): Broad restrictions applied to editing in certain contentious areas.
    *   [Contentious topics](/Wikipedia:Contentious_topics): Areas of perpetual disagreement, often requiring special oversight.
*   [Sockpuppets](/Wikipedia:Sockpuppet_investigations): The detection and dismantling of deceptive alternate accounts, a never-ending game of digital whack-a-mole.
*   [Usernames](/Wikipedia:Usernames_for_administrator_attention) ([Requests for comment](/Wikipedia:Requests_for_comment/User_names)): For when a username is problematic, offensive, or just plain confusing.
